ble\"\n|-valign=top\n!  Date\n!  Running cost\n!  What is included\n|-valign=top\n| |\n| | \u00a35\u00bd million \u2013 \u00a38 million\n| | Cost of recently completed major refits for County-class destroyers.<ref>[http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/written_answers/1974/dec/16/ships-refits#S5CV0883P0_19741216_CWA_104 Hansard HC Deb 16 December 1974 vol 883 c316W] Question to the Secretary of State for Defence about the approximate cost of a long refit of (a) a ''Leander''-class frigate and (b) a County-class destroyer, 16 December 1974.</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==Sources==\n* {{Cite book\n  |last=Brown  |first=D. K.\n  |last2=Moore  |first2=G.\n  |title=Rebuilding the Royal Navy : Warship Design Since 1945\n  |year=2003\n  |publisher=Chatham Publishing\n  |isbn=978-184832-150-2\n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |last=Friedman  |first=N.\n  |title=British Destroyers and Frigates: The Second World War and After\n  |year=2006\n  |publisher=Chatham Publishing  |location=London\n  |isbn=1861761376 \n  |ref=harv\n}}\n* {{Cite magazine\n  |first=N.  |last=Hall\n  |title=County Class Missile Destroyers\n  |magazine=Ships Monthly\n  |date=May 2008\n  |issn=0037-394X\n  |ref={{harvid|Hall (May 2008)}}\n  |pages=48\u201351\n}}\n* {{Cite magazine\n  |first=N.  |last=Hall\n  |title=County Class Missile Destroyers, HMS London role in Confrontation and Aden crisis as HMS Eagle escort 65-7.\n  |magazine=Ships Monthly\n  |date=December 2008\n  |issn=0037-394X\n  |ref={{harvid|Hall (December 2008)}}\n  |pages=50\u201351\n}}\n* {{Cite book\n  |contribution=Postwar AIO & Command Systems in the Royal Navy\n  |title=Warship 2016\n  |last=Marland  |first=P.\n  |editor-last=Jordan  |editor-first=John\n  |year=2016\n  |publisher=Conway Maritime Press\n  |isbn=1844863263\n  |pages=76\u201398\n  |ref={{harvid|Marland|2016}}\n}}\n*{{cite book |last=Marriott |first=Leo |title=Royal Navy Destroyers Since 1945 |year=1989 |publisher=Ian Allan |location=Shepperton, UK |isbn=0-711